The paper discusses image encryption algorithms based on DNA computing and chaos theory. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves information theory (cs.IT), computer vision (cs.CV), control systems (cs.SY), and multimedia (cs.MM) as these fields are relevant to the image encryption techniques discussed in the paper.
